parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in fatalities.

no warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manual transmission can cause a loss of forward propulsion, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of transmission gears can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in fatalities.
symptoms: grinding noise from under the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause a loss of control, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in fatalities.

broken or detached upper molding part of the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly design and maintain the air filters can lead to mold growth, which can cause health hazards to occupants and potentially clog the drains, resulting in flooding of the car interior and rust.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature paint chipping on the hood can lead to rust and corrosion, potentially affecting the vehicle's appearance and resale value.

The cracking of the center display screen can cause the screen to become unreadable, which can lead to a safety issue as the driver may not be able to access important information, such as navigation or safety alerts.
symptoms: The center display screen develops cracks
the screen is affected by a "spider cracking" pattern.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the blind spot sensor can cause the driver to be unaware of vehicles in their blind spot, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The blind spot sensor does not turn on
the blind spot sensor only turns on intermittently
the blind spot sensor does not provide audible or visual warnings.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Start Button and Transmission Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the engine start button and transmission can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, making it difficult or impossible to shift, and potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The red key light on the engine start button flashes
the vehicle will not turn off
the vehicle is unable to shift gears
the check engine light comes on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner compressor hose can cause the air conditioner to stop working, leading to discomfort and inconvenience for the driver and passengers.
The failure of the blind spot monitoring system can increase the risk of accidents, as the driver may not be aware of vehicles in their blind spot.
symptoms: The blind spot monitoring system disengages while driving
no warning lights or beeps are heard when the system is off
the system does not reactivate when the switch is pressed
the system only reactivates after stopping and restarting the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unsnapping of the rear window inner liner can partially block the rear view, increasing the risk of accidents.
